CREATE TABLE visibility_frames(
  id BIGSERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  agent_uid TEXT,
  ts TIMESTAMPTZ,
  procs JSONB,
  flows JSONB
);
CREATE INDEX ON visibility_frames(agent_uid, ts DESC);

prompts/backend_07_10_enforcement.md

Extend POST /assignments → accept mode and snapshot.

Validate snapshot schema; sign bundle (7.9 signer).

Store assignment + emit aegis.assignments.created.

Add GET /assignments/:id for inspection.

Acceptance: posting assignment yields agent apply + telemetry.

prompts/backend_07_10_visibility.md

Add NATS consumer for aegis.visibility.host.*; persist JSON frames.

GET /agents/:id/visibility/latest returns last frame.

